name: ACK Fried Chicken ,DAUSA,Kintamani
address: R74R+63J, Dausa, Kintamani, Bangli Regency, Bali 80652, Indonesia
review 1: The GPS location is incorrect, it is supposed to be opposite the SMKN 3 Kintamani instead of inside it, so it is at the other side of the road. The place  is quite strategic since there is no other "modern" or easy to be recognized eating place on our way to Kintamani from Tejakula. Lucky we can make a stop here, the food is quite tasty and I enjoyed the penyet (smashed) chicken. Unfortunately during our visit the toilet is broken and we need to go to SMKN 3. There are many flies also so need to keep hushing them away.
